cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.DB

The paper focuses on developing a deep learning framework for click-through rate (CTR) prediction within Tencent advertising system. This involves training probabilistic models with increasing feature embedding capabilities and implementing a parallel training system. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as these are all related to developing and improving machine learning models. Additionally, cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.DB (Databases) are also possible sub-categories as they relate to the implementation of the parallel training system and handling large datasets within the advertising system.
